        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This is handler for GIC interrupts. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>CallbackRef</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Not used in the function currently </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Loop across all the GICPx status registers and check for every set bit in them.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Disable the interrputs if the mask bit is set.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Call the corresponding the handler after disabling the interrupt.</para></listitem><listitem><para>After handler returns, clear the interrupt the status bit. </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>        </inbodydescription>
